<chapter xml:id="getting-started" xreflabel="Getting Started" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"
    xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="5.1">
    <title>Getting Started</title>
    <sect1 condition="desktop">
        <title>Main Workspace</title>
        <para>The &productshort; workspace is comprised of a <xref xlink:href="#main-menu"/> and
                <xref xlink:href="#view-panels"/>.</para>
        <sect2 xml:id="main-menu" xreflabel="Main Menu">
            <title>Main Menu</title>
            <para>Each menu on the Main Menu displays a list of menu items. Menus may be accessed
                using a mouse pointer or accelerator keys.</para>
            <variablelist>
                <varlistentry>
                    <term><guimenu>File</guimenu> (<keycombo>
                            <keycap>Alt</keycap>
                            <keycap>F</keycap>
                        </keycombo>)</term>
                    <listitem>
                        <variablelist>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>New logbook</guimenuitem> (<keycombo>
                                        <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
                                        <keycap>N</keycap>
                                    </keycombo>)</term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Starts a new empty logbook. </para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                        </variablelist>
                        <variablelist>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Open Logbook</guimenuitem> (<keycombo>
                                        <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
                                        <keycap>O</keycap>
                                    </keycombo>)</term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Displays the <guilabel>Open file</guilabel> dialog that
                                        lists previously saved logbook files and enables opening of
                                        a selected logbook file.</para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                        </variablelist>
                        <variablelist>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem> (<keycombo>
                                        <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
                                        <keycap>S</keycap>
                                    </keycombo>)</term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Saves the current open logbook.</para>
                                    <para>When a logbook has never been saved, this behaves like a
                                            <guimenuitem>Save as</guimenuitem> operation.</para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                        </variablelist>
                        <variablelist>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Save as</guimenuitem> (<keycombo>
                                        <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
                                        <keycap>V</keycap>
                                    </keycombo>)</term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Displays the Save as dialog that enables saving of the
                                        current open logbook to a new logbook file.</para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                        </variablelist>
                        <variablelist>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Open cloud storage</guimenuitem></term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Connects to the &productcloud;, fetches data and displays
                                        divelogs.</para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                        </variablelist>
                        <variablelist>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Save to cloud storage</guimenuitem></term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Connects to the &productcloud;, sends data changes to the
                                        cloud storage.</para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                        </variablelist>
                        <variablelist>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Cloud storage online</guimenuitem></term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Toggles saving of the current logbook between local cache
                                        and cloud storage.</para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                        </variablelist>
                        <variablelist>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Close</guimenuitem> (<keycombo>
                                        <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
                                        <keycap>W</keycap>
                                    </keycombo>)</term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Closes the current open logbook without exiting
                                        &productshort;</para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                        </variablelist>
                        <variablelist>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Export</guimenuitem> (<keycombo>
                                        <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
                                        <keycap>E</keycap>
                                    </keycombo>)</term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Displays the <guilabel>Export dive log files</guilabel>
                                        dialog that can be used to export &productshort; logfile
                                        format to file formats used by other divelog programs,
                                        exchange formats and presentation formats.</para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                        </variablelist>
                        <variablelist>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Print</guimenuitem> (<keycombo>
                                        <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
                                        <keycap>P</keycap>
                                    </keycombo>)</term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Displays the <guilabel>Print</guilabel> dialog that can be
                                        used to define print layout options, preview results and
                                        send data to a printer.</para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                        </variablelist>
                        <variablelist>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Preferences</guimenuitem> (<keycombo>
                                        <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
                                        <keycap>,</keycap>
                                    </keycombo>)</term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Displays the <guilabel>Preferences</guilabel> dialog that
                                        can be used to set user preferences related to various
                                        functional areas of the software.</para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                        </variablelist>
                        <variablelist>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Find moved media files</guimenuitem></term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para/>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                        </variablelist>
                        <variablelist>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Configure dive computer</guimenuitem> (<keycombo>
                                        <keycap/>
                                        <keycap>Shift</keycap>
                                        <keycap>C</keycap>
                                    </keycombo>)</term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Displays the <guilabel>Configure dive computer</guilabel>
                                        dialog that can be used to define communication and settings
                                        properties for various dive computer types.</para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                        </variablelist>
                        <variablelist>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Recent Logbooks</guimenuitem></term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Lists four of the most recent logbooks to be opened in
                                        order most to least recent.</para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                        </variablelist>
                        <variablelist>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem> (<keycombo>
                                        <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
                                        <keycap>Q</keycap>
                                    </keycombo>)</term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Terminates &productshort;.</para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                        </variablelist>
                    </listitem>
                </varlistentry>
                <varlistentry>
                    <term><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> (<keycombo>
                            <keycap>Alt</keycap>
                            <keycap>E</keycap>
                        </keycombo>)</term>
                    <listitem>
                        <variablelist>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem> (<keycombo>
                                        <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
                                        <keycap>Z</keycap>
                                    </keycombo>)</term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Reverts the most recent changes made to an unsaved logbook
                                        from most to least recent.</para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Redo</guimenuitem> (<keycombo>
                                        <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
                                        <keycap>Shift</keycap>
                                        <keycap>Z</keycap>
                                    </keycombo>)</term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Roles back most recent changes undone by an
                                            <guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem> operation to an unsaved
                                        logbook from most to least recent.</para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                        </variablelist>
                    </listitem>
                </varlistentry>
                <varlistentry>
                    <term><guimenu>Import</guimenu> (<keycombo>
                            <keycap>Alt</keycap>
                            <keycap>I</keycap>
                        </keycombo>)</term>
                    <listitem>
                        <variablelist>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Import from dive computer</guimenuitem> (<keycombo>
                                        <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
                                        <keycap>D</keycap>
                                    </keycombo>)</term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Displays the <guilabel>Download from dive
                                            computer</guilabel> dialog that enables selection of
                                        specific dive computer to download from and setting of
                                        download options.</para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Import from log files</guimenuitem> (<keycombo>
                                        <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
                                        <keycap>I</keycap>
                                    </keycombo>)</term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Displays the <guilabel>Open dive log file</guilabel>
                                        dialog that enables listing and selection of log files
                                        stored in the <application>DataTrak</application> file
                                        format.</para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Import from divelogs.de</guimenuitem></term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Displays the <guilabel>Web service connection</guilabel>
                                        dialog that enables definition of divelog.de authentication
                                        details and starting of an operation to fetch divelogs from
                                        divelog.de.</para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                        </variablelist>
                    </listitem>
                </varlistentry>
                <varlistentry>
                    <term><guimenu>Log</guimenu> (<keycombo>
                            <keycap>Alt</keycap>
                            <keycap>L</keycap>
                        </keycombo>)</term>
                    <listitem>
                        <variablelist>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Add dive</guimenuitem> (<keycombo>
                                        <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
                                        <keycap>+</keycap>
                                    </keycombo>)</term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para/>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Plan dive</guimenuitem> (<keycombo>
                                        <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
                                        <keycap>L</keycap>
                                    </keycombo>)</term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Displays the &productplanner; module that enables dive
                                        planning.</para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Edit dive in planner</guimenuitem></term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Opens a dive plan selected in the <guilabel>Dive
                                            List</guilabel> in the &productplanner; for
                                        editing.</para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Copy dive components</guimenuitem> (<keycombo>
                                        <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
                                        <keycap>C</keycap>
                                    </keycombo>)</term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Displays the <guilabel>Components selection</guilabel>
                                        dialog that enables copy of select properties of a divelog
                                        to memory from which it can be pasted into another
                                        divelog.</para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Paste dive components</guimenuitem> (<keycombo>
                                        <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
                                        <keycap>V</keycap>
                                    </keycombo>)</term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Pastes previously copied dive components into the divelog
                                        currently selected in the <guilabel>Dive
                                        List</guilabel>.</para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Renumber</guimenuitem> (<keycombo>
                                        <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
                                        <keycap>R</keycap>
                                    </keycombo>)</term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Displays the <guilabel>Renumber</guilabel> dialog that
                                        enables renumbering of all dives starting from a given
                                        number.</para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Auto group</guimenuitem></term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Groups records in the <guilabel>Dive list</guilabel> by
                                        location.</para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem>Edit device names</guimenuitem></term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Displays the <guilabel>Edit dive computer
                                            nicknames</guilabel> dialog that enables removing dive
                                        computers from a list and appending nicknames to dive
                                        computers.</para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                            <varlistentry>
                                <term><guimenuitem/> (<keycombo>
                                        <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
                                        <keycap>F</keycap>
                                    </keycombo>)</term>
                                <listitem>
                                    <para>Displays the <guilabel>Filter</guilabel> sub panel that
                                        enables the <guilabel>Dive List</guilabel> to be filtered
                                        based on Tag, Person, Location and Suits properties.</para>
                                </listitem>
                            </varlistentry>
                        </variablelist>
                    </listitem>
